---
// Video showcase section - "Obsérvanos en acción"
---

<section class="relative py-24 bg-gradient-to-b from-yellow-50 via-orange-50 to-red-50 overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Background decorative elements -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10">
        <div class="absolute top-20 left-20 w-32 h-32 bg-yellow-300 rounded-full blur-3xl animate-pulse"></div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-20 right-20 w-40 h-40 bg-orange-300 rounded-full blur-3xl animate-pulse delay-1000"></div>
        <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 w-24 h-24 bg-red-300 rounded-full blur-2xl animate-pulse delay-500"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="relative z-10 container mx-auto px-8">
        <!-- Section Header -->
        <div class="text-center mb-20">
            <h2 class="text-6xl font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-600 via-orange-600 to-red-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent mb-6">
                Obsérvanos en acción
            </h2>
            <div class="w-32 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-400 to-orange-500 rounded-full mx-auto mb-8"></div>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
                Comprueba cómo animamos el ambiente en Fallas, Moros y Cristianos, Hogueras, bodas, 
                despedidas de soltero y fiestas privadas; creando una experiencia inolvidable para todos los asistentes.
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Video Grid -->
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8 mb-16">
            <!-- Concursos Nacionales de Charangas -->
            <div class="group relative bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-2">
                <div class="aspect-video bg-gradient-to-br from-yellow-200 to-orange-200 relative overflow-hidden">
                    <!-- Video thumbnail placeholder -->
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
                        <div class="text-6xl">🏆</div>
                    </div>
                    <!-- Play button overlay -->
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/20 flex items-center justify-center opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300">
                        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-white/90 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
                            <div class="w-0 h-0 border-l-[12px] border-l-orange-600 border-t-[8px] border-t-transparent border-b-[8px] border-b-transparent ml-1"></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="p-6">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">Concursos Nacionales de Charangas</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-4">Nuestra participación en competiciones nacionales</p>
                    <a 
                        href="https://youtu.be/xNFLaF3woZw?t=30" 
                        target="_blank"
                        class="inline-flex items-center text-orange-600 font-semibold hover:text-orange-700 transition-colors"
                    >
                        Ver último concurso
                        <svg class="w-4 h-4 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Fiestas privadas -->
            <div class="group relative bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-2">
                <div class="aspect-video bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-200 to-pink-200 relative overflow-hidden">
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
                        <div class="text-6xl">🎉</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/20 flex items-center justify-center opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300">
                        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-white/90 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
                            <div class="w-0 h-0 border-l-[12px] border-l-orange-600 border-t-[8px] border-t-transparent border-b-[8px] border-b-transparent ml-1"></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="p-6">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">Fiestas privadas</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-4">Animando celebraciones íntimas y especiales</p>
                    <a 
                        href="https://youtu.be/_7_5hmK3ccM?si=sDcSvZlKAwM7p1ak" 
                        target="_blank"
                        class="inline-flex items-center text-orange-600 font-semibold hover:text-orange-700 transition-colors"
                    >
                        Ver video
                        <svg class="w-4 h-4 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Moros y Cristianos -->
            <div class="group relative bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-2">
                <div class="aspect-video bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-200 to-indigo-200 relative overflow-hidden">
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
                        <div class="text-6xl">⚔️</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/20 flex items-center justify-center opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300">
                        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-white/90 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
                            <div class="w-0 h-0 border-l-[12px] border-l-orange-600 border-t-[8px] border-t-transparent border-b-[8px] border-b-transparent ml-1"></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="p-6">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">Moros y Cristianos</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-4">Tradición y música en las fiestas valencianas</p>
                    <a 
                        href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-Qn-eYxHKj8" 
                        target="_blank"
                        class="inline-flex items-center text-orange-600 font-semibold hover:text-orange-700 transition-colors"
                    >
                        Ver video
                        <svg class="w-4 h-4 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Hogueras -->
            <div class="group relative bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-2">
                <div class="aspect-video bg-gradient-to-br from-red-200 to-orange-200 relative overflow-hidden">
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
                        <div class="text-6xl">🔥</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/20 flex items-center justify-center opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300">
                        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-white/90 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
                            <div class="w-0 h-0 border-l-[12px] border-l-orange-600 border-t-[8px] border-t-transparent border-b-[8px] border-b-transparent ml-1"></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="p-6">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">Hogueras</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-4">Celebrando las fiestas de San Juan en Alicante</p>
                    <a 
                        href="https://youtu.be/-Qn-eYxHKj8?si=veHEczXTncMXXeuc" 
                        target="_blank"
                        class="inline-flex items-center text-orange-600 font-semibold hover:text-orange-700 transition-colors"
                    >
                        Ver video
                        <svg class="w-4 h-4 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Bottom CTA -->
        <div class="text-center">
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-500 via-orange-500 to-red-500 rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-xl">
                <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
                    ¿Quieres que animemos tu próximo evento?
                </h3>
                <p class="text-yellow-100 mb-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                    Contáctanos y descubre cómo podemos hacer de tu celebración un momento inolvidable
                </p>
                <a 
                    href="https://api.whatsapp.com/send?phone=34686099729&text=%C2%A1Hola!+Estar%C3%ADa+interesado+en+contratar+una+charanga/banda+de+m%C3%BAsica,+%C2%BFpodr%C3%ADa+darme+un+presupuesto%3F"
                    class="bg-white text-orange-600 px-8 py-3 rounded-full font-semibold text-lg hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors duration-300 shadow-lg inline-block"
                >
                    Contactar ahora
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
